      <p class="f4 cl-white mt0">The classic <em>“Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&hellip;”</em> passage is attributed to a remixing of the Roman philosopher <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cicero" target="_blank" title="Marcus Tullius Cicero on Wikipedia">Cicero</a>'s 45 BC text <em>De Finibus Bonorum et Malorum (“On the Extremes of Good and Evil”)</em>. More specifically, the passage is thought to originate from sections 1.10.32 – 33 of his text, with the most notable portion excerpted below:
