      <p class="f4 cl-white mb0">According to Latin professor <a href="https://priceonomics.com/the-history-of-lorem-ipsum/" target="_blank" title="The History of Lorem Ipsum on Pricenomics">Richard McClintock</a> — the man credited with discovering Lorem Ipsum's roots — it is likely that sometime during the middle ages a typesetter scrambled part of Cicero's <em>De Finibus</em> in order to provide placeholder text to mockup various fonts for a type specimen book. But that was just the beginning.
